FoodStock

Purpose

Keep track of what groceries you have
Warns you when they're going to expire soon.

Gives you points for using groceries before they expire.


Main Activity

List of groceries you have by name.
By expiration time left.

RecyclerView
    List of grocery items.
    Each grocery item has name, expiration, and button to use.
    Clicking on button removes from list and adds points.

    Expired foods go to list of shame. Can be cleared by clicking its clear button.

    Sort by option resets recycler view and resorts.

    Menu displays current points, high score points.

    
